---
---
<section class="py-20 px-6 relative overflow-hidden">

  <!-- Gradient band -->
  <div aria-hidden="true"
       class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-neb-purple via-neb-blue to-neb-cyan opacity-90 dark:opacity-80 pointer-events-none"></div>

  <!-- Dot texture -->
  <div aria-hidden="true" class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none"
       style="background-image: radial-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.12) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 24px 24px;"></div>

  <!-- Retro scanline on band -->
  <div aria-hidden="true" class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none dark:block hidden"
       style="background: repeating-linear-gradient(0deg, transparent, transparent 3px, rgba(0,0,0,0.04) 3px, rgba(0,0,0,0.04) 6px);"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center reveal">

    <!-- Retro label -->
    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mb-5">
      <div class="w-8 h-px bg-white/60"></div>
      <span class="font-mono text-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-white/80">Cotiza sin compromiso</span>
      <div class="w-8 h-px bg-white/60"></div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="font-makoto text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-4 text-white">
      ¿LISTO PARA CREAR?
    </h2>
    <p class="text-white/85 text-lg mb-8 font-medium leading-relaxed">
      Contáctanos hoy y recibe tu cotización en minutos.<br/>
      <strong class="text-white">Tu idea merece existir.</strong>
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
      <a href="https://wa.me/573232218586?text=Hola%20Nebulab%203D%2C%20quiero%20cotizar%20un%20proyecto"
         target="_blank" rel="noopener"
         class="bg-white text-neb-ink font-bold font-mono px-8 py-4 rounded-sm text-sm
                tracking-widest uppercase pixel-corner w-full sm:w-auto text-center
                hover:bg-white/90 transition-all duration-200
                hover:shadow-[0_8px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.25)]">
        ESCRIBIR POR WHATSAPP
      </a>
      <a href="https://www.instagram.com/nebulab3d/"
         target="_blank" rel="noopener"
         class="border-2 border-white text-white font-bold font-mono px-8 py-4 rounded-sm text-sm
                tracking-widest uppercase pixel-corner w-full sm:w-auto text-center
                hover:bg-white/15 transition-all duration-200">
        VER EN INSTAGRAM
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
